Collect Sketchy Pages

Sketchy Pages (SPS) is a unique ERC721 token that can be claimed if a person owns 3 or more SABC nfts. These Sketchy Pages serve as a utility for the Sketchy Ape Book Club NFT project.

They are dynamic and can hold a message. The owner of a page can change the message anytime.

Owning one of these pages gives the owner access to participate in the original art auction of the Sketchy Ape Book Club Collection.

For the holders

Sketchy Ape Comic Club

SACC is a collection of 10,000 NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain. Each trait is meticulously hand-drawn and crafted, then generated by an algorithm to create unique art pieces.

Mint free SACC's when you hold an SABC, and stand a chance to mint one of the 7 legendaries.

MINTING will start on a specified date.
